SOCI 446	Colonialism and Society.	Forms that colonialism took, its impact on colonial societies, and its modern legacies, focusing on overseas colonialism  between 1600 and the 1970s.	0.0	Sociology (Faculty of Arts)	t	f	f	Prerequisite: SOCI 210 or permission from instructor.	\N
