POTH 685	Perception and Action.	New research concepts related to perception and action, with a special emphasis on the understanding of motor behaviour in patient populations and the exploration of potential applications in rehabilitation.	0.0	Phys and Occ Therapy (Graduate Studies)	t	f	f	Prerequisite: POTH 455 or equivalent	\N
